    <h1>About Game Calendar</h1>
    <p>Game Calendar automatically tracks upcoming video game release dates on PC, PlayStation 5, Xbox and Nintendo Switch.</p>
    <p>Data is sourced from IGDB and refreshed every six hours via an automated workflow. No editors, no articles — just dates.</p>

    <h2>How it works</h2>
    <p>An n8n workflow queries the IGDB API every six hours, normalizes the data and saves it as JSON. The site is then automatically rebuilt and published as static HTML pages on Cloudflare Pages.</p>

    <h2>The hype score</h2>
    <p>The number on each cover is derived from the number of IGDB followers and media coverage for that game. It's an estimate of anticipation, not a quality rating.</p>
